sourcesContent: import { Checkbox, Table, TextInput } from "flowbite-react" import { useRef, useState } from "react" import { useGetAllWordsQuery } from "../../app/API/wordAPI" import { Word } from "../../app/types/types" export default function AdminWordsRow(props: Word){ const {data, isSuccess} = useGetAllWordsQuery() const [eng, setEng] = useState(props.eng) const [rus, setRus] = useState(props.rus) function changeEngslih(e: any){ console.log(e) } return ( {props.id} DELETE ) }
